title: Toyota Motor Manufacturing Canada to deploy Agility Robotics’ Digit humanoids
description:
Toyota Motor Manufacturing Canada is expanding its commercial trials for Digit from three humanoids to 10.

The post Toyota Motor Manufacturing Canada to deploy Agility Robotics’ Digit humanoids appeared first on The Robot Report.
